idl_progs
useful idl scripts for use with ExoRT

makecolumn.pro                 -- create custom 1d profile for ExoCAM
getcolumn.pro                  -- grab single specified column from CESM model output and create 1D input file
plotspectra.pro                -- make plots of radiance in each spectral interval from 1D output
makeCIA.pro                    -- bin H2-H2, N2-H2, and N2-N2 CIA to ExoRT grids
cloudoptics_mie.pro            -- make cloud optical property files based on mie calculationsx
